t\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Blind</b> is a clerical <a href=\"/wiki/Monster_spell\" title=\"Monster spell\">monster spell</a> that can be cast by <a href=\"/wiki/Monster\" title=\"Monster\">monsters</a> of level 6 or higher.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Effects\">Effects</span></h2>\n<p>As its name suggests, it will <a href=\"/wiki/Blind\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Blind\">blind</a> you for 200 (more) turns; this duration is halved with <a href=\"/wiki/Half_spell_damage\" title=\"Half spell damage\">half spell damage</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Messages\">Messages</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\"Scales_cover_your_.21\">Scales cover your &lt;eyes&gt;!</span></dt>\n<dd>A monster cast the blind spell at you.</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.0_Release/src/mcastu.c#L639\">src/mcastu.c in NetHack 3.6.0, line 639</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article has been updated to reflect NetHack 3.6.4. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article has been updated to reflect NetHack 3.6.4. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/3/37/Nh364-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>This page may need to be updated for the <a href=\"/wiki/Current_version\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Current version\">current version</a>